Populations of Washington State Counties

Daniel Brusic

January 30, 2018

Below is a map of Washington State counties and their total populations according to the U.S. Census Bureaus 2010 decennial census. The data was obtained from the fact finder website for the census. Help in creating this map was obtained from leaflets tutorial website through github, and from this May 2015 blog post. Scrolling over the map with the cursor displays pop-up labels with county names and total populations, as measured in the 2010 census.
